[[英國|英國]]是世界第八大旅遊目的地國家，2014年有3440萬人外國遊客參觀英國，帶來172億美元的消費。英國旅遊局的數據顯示美國是英國最重要的客源，2010年美國人在英國消費21億英鎊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16044975|publisher=Sky News|title=Fears US Debt Crisis Will Hit UK Tourism|year=2011|accessdate=2011-08-06}}{{dead link|date=October 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。但歐洲人則在數量上取勝。前往英國的歐洲遊客數達2150萬人，而加拿大人和美國人則是350萬人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.statistics.gov.uk/cci/nugget.asp?id=352|publisher=Office for National Statistics|title=Office for National Statistics - Overseas residents' visits to the UK|year=2010|accessdate=2011-08-14|archive-date=2011-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110825143234/http://www.statistics.gov.uk/cci/nugget.asp?id=352|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。英國最受歡迎的觀光城市是倫敦，最受歡迎的景點則是[[倫敦塔|倫敦塔]]<ref name=ALVA>{{cite web|url=http://www.alva.org.uk/visitor_statistics/|title=Visits Made in 2009 to Visitor Attractions in Membership with ALVA|publisher=Association of Leading Visitor Attractions|accessdate=21 May 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101031142218/http://www.alva.org.uk/visitor_statistics/|archivedate=31 October 2010}}</ref>。此外，英國國內旅遊仍是英國旅遊業最大的客源<ref name=VB2009>''[http://www.visitbritain.org/Images/UK%20Tourist%202009_tcm139-191452.pdf UK Tourist 2009] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217185950/http://www.visitbritain.org/Images/UK%20Tourist%202009_tcm139-191452.pdf |date=2015-02-17 }}'', VisitBritain, June 2011</ref>。
